column1: SELECT  s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,  g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 limit 500000
